principles:
  - functional, no classes
  - test first, code later (TDD)
  - CLEAN is overkill and overuse layering (lasagna code)

layers:
  - database: functions that do database queires only
  - validators: functions tha throw errors based on their parameters
  - functions: functions that do any other nice stuff for us

-- Use cases --

sign up
  - validate form
  - insert on database
  - send verification mail

create post
  - clean form
  - insert on database

create comment
  - clean form
  - insert on database
  - send notification

edit post
  - clean form
  - update database

edit comment
  - clean form
  - update database

react to post
  - insert on database
  - create/update notification

follow
  - update database
  - create notification

unfollow
  - update database